sa dedom i Lukom.

7
00:00:30,764 --> 00:00:34,131
Rekli su mi su mi neke
stvari koje si im ti rekao.

8
00:00:35,603 --> 00:00:38,231
O tome kako ne eli
da ode u Rim.

9
00:00:38,405 --> 00:00:42,603
Da te u Jerusalimu
neto mnogo privlai.

10
00:00:43,511 --> 00:00:46,241
Jesi li ozbiljno to
mislio, Bazile?

11
00:00:47,481 --> 00:00:49,745
Da, jesam, Debora.

12
00:00:50,584 --> 00:00:52,950
Onda mogu da ti
ispriam za moj problem.

13
00:00:53,120 --> 00:00:57,819
Zna, deda je deponovao
veliku sumu zlata u Antiohiji

14
00:00:57,992 --> 00:01:02,122
