moe rei te rei.

36
00:03:18,899 --> 00:03:21,129
elim ti savren brak.

37
00:03:21,301 --> 00:03:22,928
Debora?

38
00:03:29,977 --> 00:03:32,844
Ne postoji pitanje braka sa njom.

39
00:03:34,415 --> 00:03:36,406
Voli li je?

40
00:03:39,019 --> 00:03:40,646
Da li?

41
00:03:43,691 --> 00:03:46,717
Da. Neu da te laem oko toga...

42
00:03:48,362 --> 00:03:50,592
ali pomoi u ti.

43
